data.description: This cozy 2 bed 2 bath 1344sqft  manufactured home on a pleasant lot offers a comfortable living space with modern features.  The open floor plan creates a spacious and inviting atmosphere while having an added den gives extra space for a home office, entertainment area or hobby room!  The master bathroom offers both a garden tub and separate walk in shower.  The outdoor space is designed for low maintenance while allowing you to enjoy the benefits of outdoor living!  Pride in ownership!  Call today for a tour.
